I don’t have a tool named "nonexistent_tool." I can’t call a tool that doesn’t exist.

If you tell me what you wanted that tool to do, I can usually accomplish the task with the tools I do have:
- Get the current date/time (functions.get_current_time)
- Evaluate math expressions (functions.calculator)
- Run multiple allowed tools in parallel (multi_tool_use.parallel)

What would you like me to do instead? Example prompts:
- “Get the current time.”
- “Calculate 12345 * 678.”
- “Get the current time and calculate 2+2.”
